name: Tezzy Everydays #10 | ALF | May 16th, 2021
description: This is the tenth day of my 1 of 1 pixel art series. Every pixel art piece will involve everyones favorite coin, which most certainly is Tezos. It was the 80's. And a young Clipdad would be sitting cross legged in his jammies, eagerly awaiting the new episode of ALF. I was captivated with the cat eating, charismatic alien from the planet Melmac alternately named Gordon Shumway. We all were...Tezzy Everydays are created by @clipdad_
